					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Set the policy value for Computer Configuration &gt;&gt; Administrative Templates &gt;&gt; Windows Components &gt;&gt; Microsoft Defender Antivirus &gt;&gt; Real-time Protection &gt;&gt; "Configure monitoring for incoming and outgoing file and program activity" to "Enabled" with a policy option value of "bi-directional (full on-access)".</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
